data.description: Discovering your dream home in today's competitive market can feel like searching for a needle in a haystack. However, I have exciting news for you! I have found a hidden gem that awaits you right now! This exquisite residence combines elegance with affordability, resembling a luxury home. With 5 BDRMS, 4 BTHS, a media & game room, plus an office that can easily double as another bedroom, this spacious haven is perfect for any size family or gathering. Whether you're hosting an NBA Finals Party, a Super Bowl Party, or any other event, the generously sized rooms can accommodate a multitude of guests. Situated on over a .25-acre lot, the property features an extended driveway & a 2-car garage. The inviting back patio is ready to be adorned with the perfect patio set, & if you desire a pool, there's ample space to build one. The backyard has been expertly designed with proper drain lines to ensure its resilience during the rainy season. Come see this stunning beauty & let's make a deal!
